<td colspan="3">Anonymous contact affiliated with Three Portlands <em>Are We Cool Yet</em> cell personally delivered document to executives of Perispirit Records division. Maximilian Driscoll, MC&amp;D representative to Perispirit Records, subsequently reviewed and logged accordingly. Any spelling and grammatical errors were present as written in the original document.</td>
