<table class="wiki-content-table">
<tr>
<th colspan="4">Memo 41</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="4">DM437/25P16F/PSR77</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Sender</th>
<td>Stuart Estes</td>
<th>Recipient</th>
<td>Millicent Concord</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="4">Customers are asking if there's any way to &quot;pause&quot; a concert and come back to it later. Making the item more convenient would help broaden the market; what's your take?</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="4">Marshall, Carter and Dark, LLP</th>
